ian Cup]]\n|<center>[[FK Partizan|Partizan]]</center>\n|<center>1\u20130</center>\n|<center>[[Red Star Belgrade]]</center>\n|7th\n|[[2017\u201318 Serbian Cup|2017\u201318]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|SVK}} [[Football in Slovakia|Slovakia]]\n|[[2018\u201319 Slovak Cup]]\n|<center>[[FC Spartak Trnava|Spartak Trnava]]</center>\n|<center>[[2019 Slovak Cup Final|3\u20133]] {{pso|4\u20131}}</center>\n|<center>[[M\u0160K \u017dilina|\u017dilina]]</center>\n|6th\n|[[1997\u201398 Slovak Cup|1997\u201398]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|SVN}} [[Football in Slovenia|Slovenia]] \n|[[2018\u201319 Slovenian Football Cup|2018\u201319 Slovenian Cup]]\n|<center>[[NK Olimpija Ljubljana|Olimpija Ljubljana]]</center>\n|<center>2\u20131</center>\n|<center>[[NK Maribor|Maribor]]</center>\n|2nd\n|[[2017\u201318 Slovenian Football Cup|2017\u201318]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Football in Spain|Spain]]\n|[[2018\u201319 Copa del Rey]]\n|<center>[[Valencia CF|Valencia]]</center>\n|<center>[[2019 Copa del Rey Final|2\u20131]]</center>\n|<center>[[FC Barcelona|Barcelona]]</center>\n|8th\n|[[2007\u201308 Copa del Rey|2007\u201308]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|SWE}} [[Football in Sweden|Sweden]]\n|[[2018\u201319 Svenska Cupen]]\n|<center>[[BK H\u00e4cken]]</center>\n|<center>[[2019 Svenska Cupen Final|3\u20130]]</center>\n|<center>[[AFC Eskilstuna]]</center>\n|2nd\n|[[2015\u201316 Svenska Cupen|2015\u201316]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|SUI}} [[Football in Switzerland|Switzerland]]\n|[[2018\u201319 Swiss Cup]]\n|<center>[[FC Basel|Basel]]</center>\n|<center>2\u20131</center>\n|<center>[[FC Thun|Thun]]</center>\n|13th\n|[[2016\u201317 Swiss Cup|2016\u201317]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|TUR}} [[Football in Turkey|Turkey]]\n|[[2018\u201319 Turkish Cup]]\n|<center>[[Galatasaray S.K.|Galatasaray]]</center>\n|<center>[[2019 Turkish Cup Final|3\u20131]]</center>\n|<center>[[Akhisar Belediyespor|Akhisarspor]]</center>\n|18th\n|[[2015\u201316 Turkish Cup|2015\u201316]]\n|-\n|{{flagicon|UKR}} [[Football in Ukraine|Ukraine]]\n|[[2018\u201319 Ukrainian Cup]]\n|<cen