xico|Mexico]]\n| [[2018\u201319 Liga MX Femenil season#Torneo Clausura|2019 Liga MX Femenil Clausura]]\n| align=center | [[Tigres UANL (Women)|Tigres UANL]]\n| align=center | [[C.F. Monterrey (Women)|Monterrey]]\n| 2nd\n| [[2017\u201318 Liga MX Femenil season#Torneo Clausura|2018 Clausura]]\n|-\n| [[2019\u201320 Liga MX Femenil season#Torneo Apertura|2019 Liga MX Femenil Apertura]]\n| align=center | [[C.F. Monterrey (women)|Monterrey]]\n| align=center | [[Tigres UANL (Women)|Tigres UANL]]\n| 1st\n| None\n|-\n| {{flagicon|USA}} [[Women's soccer in the United States|United States]]\n| [[2019 National Women's Soccer League season|2019 NWSL]]\n| align=center | [[North Carolina Courage]]\n| align=center | [[Chicago Red Stars]]\n| 2nd\n| [[2018 National Women's Soccer League season|2018]]\n|}\n\n===[[CONMEBOL]]===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Nation\n! Tournament\n! Champion\n! Second place\n! data-sort-type=\"number\"|Title\n! Last honor\n|-\n| {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Women's football in Brazil|Brazil]]\n| [[2019 Campeonato Brasileiro de Futebol Feminino]]\n|[[Associa\u00e7\u00e3o Ferrovi\u00e1ria de Esportes (women)|Ferrovi\u00e1ria]]\n|[[Sport Club Corinthians Paulista (women's football)|Corinthians]]\n|2nd\n|2014\n|}\n\n=== [[Oceania Football Confederation|OFC]] ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Nation\n!Tournament\n!Champion\n!Second place\n!data-sort-type=\"number\"|Title\n!Last honor\n|-\n|{{flagicon|NZL}} [[Women's football in New Zealand|New Zealand]]\n|[[2019 National Women's League (New Zealand)|2019 National Women's League]]\n|<center>[[Canterbury United Pride]]</center>\n|<center>[[Northern Football Federation|Northern Lights]]</center>\n|4th\n|[[2016 National Women's League (New Zealand)|2016]]\n|}\n\n==Women's cups==\n\n===[[UEFA]]===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Nation\n!Tournament\n!Champion\n!Final score\n!Second place\n!data-sort-type=\"number\"|Title\n!Last honor\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |{{Flagicon|ENG}} [[Women's football in Engl